data.description: Serenity and views! Come and get cozy in this 2 bed, 1.5-bathroom townhouse.  The entry level has  the 2 car garage, laundry room . The second level has a half bath, the living room w/ fireplace, the kitchen and a deck off of the dining area which boasts gorgeous views of the bay and the lush greenery of Hercules. Two bedrooms and a full bath are also on this level. There is a community pool and tennis court. Shopping, restaurants and schools are in close proximity.
